{
  "texts": [
    "Apart from that, no explicit condition was set for the interview participants.",
    "We have asked the users questions related to their (i) social media usage time and patterns (i.e., what they like to do there), (ii) their views on the content suggestions on Facebook, (iii) their opinions on the need for explainable recommendations, (iv) how they would like to view the explanations, and (v) how explanations may affect their usage of the platform.",
    "We considered the nature of Facebook content suggestions during the interview session.",
    "We have previously learned that content suggestions can vary from person to person (Chang et al., 2023).",
    "Sometimes, the suggestions are relevant to day-to-day usage; in other cases, however, the suggestions are strange and unexpected."
  ]
}